OL,6,FSo too are her tears.
OL,8,F"I wish I could go back to school. To
OL,9,Fplay with my friends," she told ITV
OL,10,FNews.
OL,12,FShe's one of many thousands of Gazan
OL,13,Fchildren who have spent a year on the
OL,14,Frun from Israeli missiles.
OL,16,FShe now lives in a tent in the
OL,17,Fsouthern city of Khan Younis; one of
OL,18,Fmany camps for displaced people.
