OL,6,FWho knows when she'll need to move
OL,7,Fagain? Who knows if she'll ever be
OL,8,Fable to return to her home in Rafa?
OL,9,F"The treatment she needs is to feel
OL,10,Fsafe," her mother said.
OL,12,F"She can't keep hearing the bombing
OL,13,Fand the sounds of ambulances. My
OL,14,Fdaughter needs her childhood back."
OL,16,FAccording to the Disasters Emergency
OL,17,FCommittee:
